00:59.200 --> 01:02.420
Bleakness is the reason
for the film, darling.

01:02.520 --> 01:04.260
That's why it exists.

01:04.360 --> 01:05.820
Yeah, yeah, look,

01:05.920 --> 01:09.180
I understand it's an important
piece of cinema for you, man,

01:09.280 --> 01:11.260
but, like, the reality is it's
actually kind of problematic.

01:11.360 --> 01:14.860
Oh, Boz,
everything's problematic

01:14.960 --> 01:16.260
if you want it
to be problematic.

01:16.360 --> 01:17.420
It's problematic.

01:17.520 --> 01:20.220
