the world's worst mother.

02:06.240 --> 02:08.620
Yeah, well, you know,
I'm the world's worst aunt.

02:08.720 --> 02:10.760
And sister. And baker.

02:11.800 --> 02:13.740
-I'll text them.
-What, and say what?

02:13.840 --> 02:15.740
