this never happened

02:25.080 --> 02:26.420
and we never
talk about it again.

02:26.520 --> 02:28.940
Yes. Good plan.

02:29.040 --> 02:31.900
I mean, at the end of the day,
we're adults, they're adults.

02:32.000 --> 02:34.020
It's my kitchen, it's my house.

02:34.120 --> 02:36.740
If they're gonna sneak around
unannounced, then it's on them.

02:36.840 --> 02:39.360
Yeah. And maybe, in a way,
this is good.

02:40.440 --> 02:42.380
Well, now we don't have to
tell them about us.

02:42.480 --> 02:44.420
Yeah.

02:44.520 --> 02:47.600
