what she's like now,

03:58.680 --> 04:00.380
what's it gonna be like
once it's here?

04:00.480 --> 04:02.960
But I thought I was just
the sperm donor, aren't I?

04:05.920 --> 04:07.460
Sometimes I just wanna
run away, you know?

04:07.560 --> 04:11.100
