can handle it.

04:14.560 --> 04:16.100
I know you can.

04:16.200 --> 04:17.500
We can?

04:17.600 --> 04:19.600
Yeah.

04:20.640 --> 04:23.540
Talia and Ariel.

04:23.640 --> 04:25.500
-Mmm.
-(CHUCKLES)

04:25.600 --> 04:27.780
