of a UK law degree.

09:04.280 --> 09:05.900
-Are you nuts?
-Objection.

09:06.000 --> 09:07.500
Overruled.

09:07.600 --> 09:09.180
Vince, I've read
a million articles

09:09.280 --> 09:10.860
