09:27.560 --> 09:30.820
What happens
if Talia and Ariel split up?

09:30.920 --> 09:34.340
The donor can get frozen out,
Vince, and never see the child.

09:34.440 --> 09:36.440
Ever.

09:36.960 --> 09:38.860
Am I the first person
you've spoken to about this?

09:38.960 --> 09:40.960
What does your mum think?

09:41.840 --> 09:45.260
