Y...you still haven't told her?

09:45.360 --> 09:47.360
Vince.

09:48.720 --> 09:49.940
(SIGHS)

09:50.040 --> 09:53.340
See how gentle I'm being
with Rory?

09:53.440 --> 09:57.060
